

Components
==========

Components are used to describe a piece of the interface. These are simply Javascript function but it returns a Reace Element.


Components Instance
-------------------

As components are the description  of a UI so we can think that a component is a template through which the whole appp is made

Properties of a Component Instance
-----------------------------------

-->Component Instances are actual physical manifestations of a component

-->A Component Instance has its own state and props.

--> A Component instance has a lifecycle. i.e it can be born, live and die